{"tid":598817,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【擱置海外掛牌？】WSJ：沙特阿美僅在當地上市","createTime":"2018-03-20T00:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T00:52:16.000Z","uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e1d0518ab87170411126237fb74c88e476a27b9c","tid":598817,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T00:47:56.000Z","msg":"【擱置海外掛牌？】WSJ：沙特阿美僅在當地上市<br />\n<br />\n【國際】 30分鐘前<br />\n<br />\n0<br />\n<br />\n【Now財經台】據《華爾街日報》引述沙特政府官員及知情人士透露，沙特政府計劃縮減國營石油公司沙特阿美的上市規模，最新計劃是明年僅在沙特證券交易所上市。<br />\n報道指，沙特政府需要更多時間決定是否在海外上市，部分原因是擔心法律風險，加上更大規模上市的必要性，已被油價上升的因素抵銷。<br />\n此外，美國財經頻道CNBC引述消息指，現階段沙特阿美只會推進在沙特證券交易所上市，最快今年下半年掛牌，至於海外上市計劃暫時擱置。<br />\n消息傳出後，沙特阿美發聲明指，仍繼續審視上市選項，考慮多個海外上市地點的可能性。<br />\n沙特政府計劃出售沙特阿美5%股權，於沙特及海外市場上市，原本目標是年底上市，倫敦、紐約及香港<br />\n交易所均力爭這單大生意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb2ed29fc739b36afc19841559a7cec141464dc","tid":598817,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T00:48:55.000Z","msg":"油王又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac1c34ef99a07176ca3f662e467f885ac33ec0f","tid":598817,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T00:50:08.000Z","msg":"388 rip"},{"pid":"3a3868d0e5e8de320a5ceb0222ea6c48896e371d","tid":598817,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aac1c34ef99a07176ca3f662e467f885ac33ec0f","tid":598817,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T00:50:08.000Z","msg":"388 rip"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T00:51:39.000Z","msg":"唔驚 我地有平保qq<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a84db061c5a7f4c909f44073fe1d4e84c6c4d4d","tid":598817,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0